{"tid":38522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"繼Gary之後】又少兩個！ 智孝、金鐘國退出《Running Man","createTime":"2016-12-14T03:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T04:10:40.000Z","uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2a3822e8150fc12acf5b74d8e52b75a899d475","tid":38522,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:37:47.000Z","msg":"繼Gary之後】又少兩個！ 智孝、金鐘國退出《Running Man》<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-14 10:33:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣綜藝節目《Running Man》深受亞洲觀眾歡迎，不過今年10月底先有成員Gary退出，令所有粉絲都晴天霹靂。<br />\n<br />\n不過今日韓國方面再爆出驚人消息，就連成員宋智孝同金鐘國都鐵定退出，並會加入新成員。<br />\n<br />\n而智孝同金鐘國方面已直認會退出節目，金鐘國方面將於下周一進行最後錄影，以後集中個人活動，智孝方面亦回應：「確定將下車，以後集中於演員活動。」<br />\n<br />\n而隨住兩人都退出，《RM》將只剩劉在錫、HaHa、池錫辰及李光洙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一早當gary走果集係最後一集RM"},{"pid":"dd280f85cf33245cbb5997f3c5e240b3ff421dc0","tid":38522,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"d342ae7242f9db962bc0c8b7bedf2082279f8879","tid":38522,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ok</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d39deaf8f8a3e511793ed233396e65d7b56f6cb2","tid":38522,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:40:31.000Z","msg":"韓國人氣綜藝節目《Running Man》（RM）今日爆出成員宋智孝及金鐘國將會退出節目，令粉絲大呼可惜。<br />\n<br />\n節目組方面就表示《RM》將於明年1月投入新一季嘅製作，節目形式亦會有新變化。隨住宋智孝、金鐘國嘅退出，成員有機會大換血，節目組亦表示會孝慮加入新成員。<br />\n<br />\n據指首名將會加入嘅就係主持人姜虎東，而姜虎東所屬事務社就表示：「的確收到《RM》製作組加盟節目嘅提案，目前積極討論中。」似乎加入嘅可能性極高。假如姜虎東加入節目，就係姜虎東同劉在錫繼2003年播出嘅人氣綜藝節目《X-MAN》後再度合作。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦有報道指諧星朴明秀亦會加盟第二季嘅《RM》，不過朴明秀方面就表示唔係事實：「純屬誤報，無論係提案定討論從來都冇過。」"},{"pid":"facb956d5b65a6b5ce0734ccd60b99b1112a4629","tid":38522,"uid":31593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"Running man 2= 愛回家2<br />\n已經唔再同原本嘅一樣"},{"pid":"88ee093daf938bc4bcf68d20c937b1b9d5a9d452","tid":38522,"uid":13770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"好快沒落"}]}